00:10:07.500 --> 00:10:09.140
They estimated that they would lose 60%

00:10:09.140 --> 00:10:11.100
to 80% of iPhone search traffic if

00:10:11.100 --> 00:10:11.860
they didn't do this.

00:10:11.960 --> 00:10:14.300
Not because people would switch to Bing, but

00:10:14.300 --> 00:10:16.880
because people just use whatever is already there.

00:10:17.100 --> 00:10:19.860
Now, see all these examples and visuals that

