design,

00:17:18.320 --> 00:17:19.180
engineering, and psychology

00:17:19.180 --> 00:17:20.920
of the tech that we use every day.

00:17:21.100 --> 00:17:23.220
And how even things that look so simple

00:17:23.220 --> 00:17:23.760
and stupid

00:17:23.760 --> 00:17:25.620
hide an absurd amount of complexity.

